186
00:13:45,189 --> 00:13:46,289
Saya sudah dikonfirmasi, kan?

187
00:13:46,289 --> 00:13:48,488
Dia bekerja di Hanul Centre.

188
00:13:48,689 --> 00:13:51,858
Lalu, siapa yang mengirim pesan sebagai Red Cry?

189
00:13:52,628 --> 00:13:53,628
Bukankah aneh?

190
00:13:53,628 --> 00:13:56,069
