207
00:15:00,529 --> 00:15:02,299
Dia mengaku sebelum meninggal?

208
00:15:03,569 --> 00:15:05,138
Aku tidak bisa mengerti.

209
00:15:06,998 --> 00:15:08,238
Kupikir dia mencoba ...

210
00:15:08,939 --> 00:15:10,478
